label.value: amyloid-beta precursor protein sequence variant (human)

value.value: An amyloid-beta precursor protein (human) that has at least one amino acid residue that differs from the corresponding residue found in another amyloid-beta precursor protein (human) when such a difference arises as the result of genetic differences, i.e., different alleles of amyloid-beta precursor protein (human). Operationally, this means the sequence representation of the amyloid-beta precursor protein (human) has at least one amino acid residue that differs from the corresponding residue found of the amino acid sequence represented by UniProtKB:P05067-1.

label.value: amyloid-beta precursor protein sequence variant (mouse)

value.value: An amyloid-beta precursor protein (mouse) that has at least one amino acid residue that differs from the corresponding residue found in another amyloid-beta precursor protein (mouse) when such a difference arises as the result of genetic differences, i.e., different alleles of amyloid-beta precursor protein (mouse). Operationally, this means the sequence representation of the amyloid-beta precursor protein (mouse) has at least one amino acid residue that differs from the corresponding residue found of the amino acid sequence represented by UniProtKB:P12023-1.
